{"tid":1106299,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS防彈少年團登美雜誌封面　RM：被稱「21世紀披頭四」感尷尬","createTime":"2019-04-14T13:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T15:16:27.000Z","uid":231132,"like":13,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e865594fc579f18da5aad8de2a0d0fed9939976d","tid":1106299,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2620518/org/935787259c7ce8864750d289b2ba6f36.jpg/BCyzJMQEPBcPKio_C_x2c6hxuiSQsTcim2X4sptl-LI?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2620518%2Forg%2F935787259c7ce8864750d289b2ba6f36.jpg%2FBCyzJMQEPBcPKio_C_x2c6hxuiSQsTcim2X4sptl-LI%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=627522d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBTS防彈少年團登上今期《Entertainment Weekly》的封面，配合彩色的背景設計，盡顯7位成員私下的少男味。接受雜誌訪問時，BTS防彈少年團除了分享自己喜愛的歌曲電影，又教海外粉絲韓式潮語外，更兩次講到有關內褲的話題。其中被問到台上發生過的尷尬事時，RM就話：「演唱會的話，內褲的顏色非常重要。我們盡量會穿黑色，但有時穿上白或紅色的話，便會發生尷尬的事，透過拉鏈&hellip;」話未說完，害羞的RM就以笑完結話題。可見台上台風十足的BTS防彈少年團，私下也只是常互相打鬧的青少年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2620518/org/935787259c7ce8864750d289b2ba6f36.jpg/BCyzJMQEPBcPKio_C_x2c6hxuiSQsTcim2X4sptl-LI?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2620518%2Forg%2F935787259c7ce8864750d289b2ba6f36.jpg%2FBCyzJMQEPBcPKio_C_x2c6hxuiSQsTcim2X4sptl-LI%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=627522d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當RM提到有關內褲顏色的話題，旁邊的Jimin不禁「Wow」一聲回應。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2620426/org/554f0ae2f467bbbd8e16c625bf16e3be.jpg/HST85kUf1lP9PxOn-9vMPiKHAWbvmIr4CtRk6ArUZOg?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2620426%2Forg%2F554f0ae2f467bbbd8e16c625bf16e3be.jpg%2FHST85kUf1lP9PxOn-9vMPiKHAWbvmIr4CtRk6ArUZOg%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=44401a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBTS防彈少年團介紹韓式潮語時，J-Hope突然大爆自己正穿着藍色內褲。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\nBTS防彈少年團近兩年人氣風靡全球，更被稱為「21世紀披頭四」。可是對於這個讚賞，RM就坦言很尷尬，但不介紹別人稱呼他們男子樂團、男子團體或韓流。訪問中提及BTS防彈少年團，因擁有與其他韓國組合不同的魅力，著重通過歌曲帶出有主題的信息，Suga謙虛地表示要有運氣的幫助。對於上年在各個國際頒獎禮上有好成績，RM就講到：「其實身為一個亞洲組合更困難，這些都是我們的目標，可是這只是目標，我們不想改變自己的身份或真實性，來獲得第一名，就如我們突然唱英語歌曲或改變了其他，就不再是BTS防彈少年團了。」表達出不想與他人比較，但仍會堅守「BTS」的本份去努力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2620438/org/bcc91f933620c7745482d3a103482552.jpg/zYULR9tVXOP24B1VeSRLWJ15a2fRqV6rfRG51n0RudY?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2620438%2Forg%2Fbcc91f933620c7745482d3a103482552.jpg%2FzYULR9tVXOP24B1VeSRLWJ15a2fRqV6rfRG51n0RudY%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=99bf60f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於「21世紀披頭四」的美譽，RM直言覺得尷尬，表現謙虛。（影片截圖）<br />\n<br />\n香港01有限公司版權所有 &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"ae49b1bb3d1f52f1e2cd2b0bda32d97a97095e2b","tid":1106299,"uid":61748,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99291ee95a20bff107047cf66a98bad79a78469f","tid":1106299,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"be humble🙏"},{"pid":"00359390d448d3b1e6819a070e03c803becaaccb","tid":1106299,"uid":76399,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMDdOwo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMDdOwo.png&h=adb831b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf58de77e493fe43ccb65e8102ed12104470a101","tid":1106299,"uid":165368,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae49b1bb3d1f52f1e2cd2b0bda32d97a97095e2b","tid":1106299,"uid":61748,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T13:26:27.000Z","msg":"j開頭都係靚仔靚女 Jisoo jimin jin<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938af6b4f8f6128b659fe01bbbee01a474df10a2","tid":1106299,"uid":143093,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cf58de77e493fe43ccb65e8